OL,3,CCar cloning: What is the crime and why
OL,4,Cis it on the rise?
OL,6,FThe is warning that car cloning is on
OL,7,Fthe rise, as the cost of car ownership
OL,8,Fgrows, and criminals look for new ways
OL,9,Fto get around cheaply while evading
OL,10,Froad tax or penalty notices.
OL,12,FSimon Williams from the company said:
OL,13,F"From data the RAC has seen there has
OL,14,Fdefinitely been a rise in car cloning,
OL,15,Fthe enemy of the modern motorist.
OL,17,F"It shouldn't really be possible, but
OL,18,Fclearly it is."
