OL,3,CCar cloning: What is the crime and why
OL,4,Cis it on the rise?
OL,6,FCar cloning ` or vehicle identity
OL,7,Ftheft ` is when a car is given a
OL,8,Fcopied or stolen number plate to make
OL,9,Fit look like another vehicle of the
OL,10,Fsame make, model and colour.
OL,12,FIt means that any crimes committed
OL,13,Fusing the cloned car will lead back to
OL,14,Fthe owner of the car with the legally
OL,15,Fregistered licence plate and hide the
OL,16,Fidentity of the real criminal.
