OL,3,CCar cloning: What is the crime and why
OL,4,Cis it on the rise?
OL,6,FCriminals might use the car to avoid
OL,7,Fspeeding fines and parking tickets.
OL,8,FThey may use fake number plates to
OL,9,Fsell a stolen car to an unsuspecting
OL,10,Fbuyer.
OL,12,FThey could also use cloned cars to
OL,13,Fcommit more serious crimes like bank
OL,14,Frobberies.
