OL,3,CCar cloning: What is the crime and why
OL,4,Cis it on the rise?
OL,6,FThe DVLA advises victims of car
OL,7,Fcloning to to return any fines or
OL,8,Fletters to the issuing authority -
OL,9,Fwith evidence to prove it was not them
OL,10,Fbehind the wheel.
OL,12,FThey should also write to the DVLA
OL,13,Fwith a crime reference number after
OL,14,Freporting it to the police.
